reviewText: Bought for my fiance. He loved it.

Duck Dynasty is a reality tv show on A&E that never gets old. The range of characters have progressed over the last seasons and shown dedication to family, faith, and to life. It's a great show that can teach you many life lessons directly and indirectly, while staying humourous.
My wife and I love Duck Dynasty and we wanted all of them on Blu-Ray disc
Love this show. Starting my collection.
I purchased this Blu-ray as a Christmas gift for my niece.  She loves it.
Great DVD of the Robinsons.  Just basic fun, humor, wit and sarcasm. Phils philosophy is spot on.  A great show to watch on DVD.  Si is the best.
